00:53:27.400 --> 00:53:31.320
We went to the doctors every week, and I would miss work just to take her.

00:53:32.280 --> 00:53:36.599
They helped her with her therapy, and I had to do a lot of things for her at home.

00:53:37.480 --> 00:53:43.880
The doctors wanted to keep me for some medical experiments, but my mom flat out refused to accept

00:53:43.880 --> 00:53:51.710
that idea. But thankfully, my mind is normal. Although some of my friends tell me I have a few

00:53:51.710 --> 00:54:00.429
screws loose, but I don't think so. As far as growing up in the neighborhood in Turillo,

00:54:00.429 --> 00:54:05.469
everything was normal. I used to fight with my brothers all the time, and I played with all the

00:54:05.469 --> 00:54:11.789
kids in the neighborhood. Then one day, the brothers came preaching door to door.

00:54:14.400 --> 00:54:20.320
So we started the study, and things progressed. I used to ask myself,

00:54:21.119 --> 00:54:25.519
how am I going to teach her to handle the Bible if she can't use her hands?

00:54:26.719 --> 00:54:32.320
About what I didn't know was how well she could use her tongue. I would say to scripture,

00:54:32.960 --> 00:54:38.079
and she would look it up with her tongue. Many times she would find it before I did.

00:54:40.159 --> 00:54:46.000
It all happened gradually, but I knew that what I was learning was very valuable. I can't say it was

00:54:46.000 --> 00:54:51.440
because of one particular scripture or anything like that. It was really just getting to know the

00:54:51.440 --> 00:54:57.519
very personality of Jehovah and the way the brothers and sisters treated me. In order to go to the

00:54:57.519 --> 00:55:03.199
kingdom hall or to the assemblies, the brothers have to carry me. And of course, as I kept growing,

00:55:03.199 --> 00:55:09.840
I got heavier and heavier. So that was an easy, you know. When I got baptized, I had affection for

00:55:09.840 --> 00:55:15.920
Jehovah, but as I kept growing spiritually and getting to know him better, I began to really

00:55:15.920 --> 00:55:24.409
treasure the privilege of serving him. The idea of talking to others made me feel terrified,

00:55:24.409 --> 00:55:31.289
scared to death, and all panicky. But all the encouragement I got from the brothers,

00:55:31.289 --> 00:55:36.650
friends, traveling overseers, and all the assistants my mom has given me were a big help.

00:55:37.369 --> 00:55:44.250
Now I really love preaching door to door. I have a little list of phone numbers that I've

00:55:44.250 --> 00:55:50.090
put together from homes in our congregation's territory. The eagle that know me have come up to me

00:55:50.090 --> 00:55:54.969
and said, I got a phone call from your daughter the other day. And I was like, what? My daughter?

00:55:57.210 --> 00:56:03.530
The sisters are so kind and they support me by bringing some of their Bible studies to my house

00:56:03.530 --> 00:56:09.289
so that I can share with them in the study. What I can't do with my hands, I can do almost

00:56:09.289 --> 00:56:22.539
almost anything with my tongue. I type on the computer with a pencil or pen. And then when it's ready,

00:56:23.260 --> 00:56:32.329
I print it, fold it, and put it into an envelope. Then I take it to sisters at the kingdom hall.

00:56:32.329 --> 00:56:37.210
They're my secretaries and they leave it at night at homes where the householders are out working.

00:56:40.460 --> 00:56:44.780
It really makes you happy because you know it makes others happy.

00:56:46.539 --> 00:56:52.139
I left a letter that Sabina had written with an unmarried couple. They made arrangements right

00:56:52.139 --> 00:57:00.619
away to please Jehovah and were legally married. Jehovah has been so kind to me. You know,

00:57:02.139 --> 00:57:06.860
when your handicapped and someone helps you or you're an older person and you get the necessary

00:57:06.860 --> 00:57:15.260
help, that really changes your life in an incredible way. I would not put it some people think they

00:57:15.260 --> 00:57:20.300
have to go and encourage her. But when they get there, the opposite happens. She's the one that

00:57:20.300 --> 00:57:31.760
encourages them. Do not be afraid for I am with you. Do not gaze about for I am your God.

00:57:34.000 --> 00:57:44.320
I will fortify you. I will really help you. I will really keep fast hold of you with my right

00:57:44.320 --> 00:57:55.289
hand of righteousness. Sister Sabina Hernandez has been approved this month as an auxiliary pioneer.

